title: Stock market news live updates: Stocks fall after Russia-Ukraine ceasefire talks fail, red-hot CPI print - Yahoo Finance
content: Stock market news live updates: Stocks fall after Russia-Ukraine ceasefire talks fail, red-hot CPI print  Yahoo Finance
description: U.S. equity futures ticked lower ahead of Tuesday's open after peace talks between Russia and Ukraine's foreign ministers failed to make progress on negotiating a ceasefire.
